{"tid":1892671,"cid":36,"subCid":0,"title":"武漢肺炎過後 你地仲會唔會維持住依加嘅衛生意識同消毒措施？","createTime":"2020-02-22T16:30:40.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-22T23:55:02.000Z","uid":26418,"like":35,"dislike":11,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"04b98821dca93068e410496a842a70bcb585d491","tid":1892671,"uid":26418,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-22T16:30:40.000Z","msg":"先講講我自己<br />\n未有武漢肺炎之前<br />\n已經每晚用酒精抹電話/鍵盤/滑鼠<br />\n食任何野之前都會用鹼液洗手/酒精搓手液消毒雙手<br />\n自己有病/流感高峰期搭公共交通工具都會戴口罩<br />\n每晚用漂白水抹地 等等<br />\n以前仲會俾人問我係咪有潔癖<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n覺得我好ON9 洗唔洗咁誇張<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n利申：90後 對沙士有少少印象<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/treat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />會 其實本身就應該要衛生啲 周圍都好多菌 而且好多人衛生意識好差<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />唔會 反正都唔會致命 最多咪腸胃炎 做咁多措施好麻煩"},{"pid":"8f7575d6f756f75343624c5c6150070196868227","tid":1892671,"uid":124899,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-22T16:32:18.000Z","msg":"會叫雞。"},{"pid":"03efe4a3d54e8c86a21cb7e95dd8d5b7ff0a4ba7","tid":1892671,"uid":199162,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-22T16:33:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4090eb83c494a1580e8c405128a80a1eee799544","tid":1892671,"uid":26418,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-22T16:33:25.000Z","msg":"諗起啲啊叔揸完水唔洗手直接行出廁所<br />\n跟住又係咁咳又多痰<br />\n跟住上巴士同你扶同一個扶手<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"81e6dc998008a6d9ad3313d4134268822ec0f994","tid":1892671,"uid":37869,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-22T16:34:41.000Z","msg":"梗係唔會啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e10938bf7d3ab27b2a0a5b0b25ef8bc5cb865abb","tid":1892671,"uid":26418,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-22T16:36:17.000Z","msg":"又或者係有個本身有病嘅人<br />\n喺間餐廳到食飯 但食緊飯嘅時候有咳<br />\n咁啲餐廳會擺定啲餐具喺檯面（已經未計餐廳洗得唔乾淨）<br />\n你會唔會就咁攞啲餐具黎食飯<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c194eec94e0b252f9c08b34893120560db6e63a3","tid":1892671,"uid":26418,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"03efe4a3d54e8c86a21cb7e95dd8d5b7ff0a4ba7","tid":1892671,"uid":199162,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-22T16:33:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-22T16:43:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9069ede87d4d1227b75c884ab049b1b599dbd003","tid":1892671,"uid":199670,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-22T16:44:27.000Z","msg":"想救立場、蘋果之類既就睇一睇 改一改<br />\n<br />\n1.喺連登貼新聞貼返link 比人賺click rate廣告費 (只限非親共/黃營媒體)同埋盡量唔好講哂所有內容 鼓勵人click入去睇<br />\n<br />\n2.見到內容農場文唔好理 尢其fb好多文宣大台都係咁 仲好多時cap圖抄新聞就算 link都唔比<br />\n<br />\n3.未fact check既野保持距離 避免過於肯定 保持獨立思考 杜絕假新聞 不要過於相信陰謀論<br />\n<br />\n第1、2點例如 金水、香港地、巴打絲打facebook club呢啲最鍾意cap新聞圖就post上去 搞到蘋果立場冇哂錢賺<br />\n<br />\n［慶祝夠未］警 世 文！一齊打返起文宣戰線好嗎<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1890283\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1890283</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"46aecdcab9a1b94b41355985189101dec20d2df4","tid":1892671,"uid":278765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-22T16:46:04.000Z","msg":"樓主個問題問得太早。<br />\n要保到命(染或不染病)捱到疫情過去/疫苖解藥應市，先至問呢個問題<br />\n<br />\np.s. 擔心香港條curve 係step-up concave / exponential，病發由cluster &rarr; random&hellip;&hellip;<br />\n<br />\n希望手足好運！"},{"pid":"f9ed98ade69c89bd5680c44af5f50191a8323d93","tid":1892671,"uid":217376,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-22T16:46:43.000Z","msg":"會，電話呢啲成日接觸嘅嘢點都會消毒乾淨"},{"pid":"670c3c0692892fbb8e5140f482461dd7fa9f36ac","tid":1892671,"uid":182222,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,